In collaboration with @jvn, we are donating $5 for every comment to local Texas mutual aids, up to $20,000. Let us know how you’re interested in getting involved in the comments, or just leave a ❤️ to show your support. 

Let’s talk about mutual aid. Mutual aid is a voluntary reciprocal exchange of resources and services for mutual benefit. It’s community care, at its finest. A few ways you can get involved with mutual aid:

- Find your local chapter and donate time or money
- Give extra groceries or goods to your local community refrigerator or food bank
- Share about mutual aid. Spreading awareness matters!

For more information we encourage you to listen to JVN’s Getting Curious podcast and discover more resources here: https://skl.sh/3gQTvyk

In Self-Care Essentials: Your Ultimate Playbook, JVN (@jvn) shares approachable tools to help you greet every day with authenticity, integrity, and joy. Curate an at-home spa moment, organize your thoughts with a self-care journal, or unwind with yoga! For more from JVN's new class arriving next week, follow his teacher page: https://skl.sh/3gn9fYt

Take 9 minutes for yourself today with these self-care exercises from some of our favorite Skillshare teachers. Once you’re done, follow the links below to see their full classes!

Exercise 1: Use inspiration from a quote to explore your experiences and perspective. @YasmineCheyenne http://skl.sh/3jZ6yOb

Exercise 2: Curate a pleasure playlist. @EugenaWashington http://skl.sh/3bjgWvU

Exercise 3: Channel your authentic voice to celebrate yourself. @theslumflower http://skl.sh/3aw0IQU

For more creative inspiration during #BlackHistoryMonth, join our weekly series My Creative Roots to learn from Skillshare teachers, their icons, and get a chance to win a year of Skillshare free! http://skl.sh/2ZnBvC6

Every creative work you've ever loved has a hero's journey behind it. The first spark. The endless iteration. The inevitable setbacks. The magical people who appear to help. And the breakthrough idea.

What really happened to them on the road to success? You’re about to find out.

Spark & Fire is a WaitWhat original series in partnership with @Skillshare.
